<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Sounds More Fun Than Living."/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="生きているより楽しそう"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="RIM"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="理芽"/><amll:meta key="album" value="NEW ROMANCER2"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPY392301530"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2105704316"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="002RZRnv4SVvHA"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="455570259"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="7qVDiEZKBR3wo43XSNv6aB"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1719622058"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:43.480"><div begin="7.530" end="3:43.480"><p begin="7.530" end="12.980" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="7.530" end="7.990">千</span><span begin="7.990" end="8.300">年</span><span begin="8.300" end="8.520">も</span><span begin="8.520" end="9.000">前</span><span begin="9.000" end="9.220">か</span><span begin="9.220" end="9.450">ら</span><span begin="9.450" end="9.990">皆</span><span begin="9.990" end="10.080">、</span><span begin="10.080" end="10.440">知</span><span begin="10.440" end="10.610">っ</span><span begin="10.610" end="10.870">て</span><span begin="10.870" end="11.100">い</span><span begin="11.100" end="12.980">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">早在千年前大家便已心知肚明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">早在千年前大家便已心知肚明</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Everyone has known since a thousand years ago,</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">천 년도 전부터 모두, 알고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout le monde le sait depuis mille ans,</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Desde hace mil años todos, lo saben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schon seit tausend Jahren wissen alle, davon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desde mil anos atrás, todos sabem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da mille anni tutti, lo sanno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sennen mo mae kara minna, shitteiru</span></p><p begin="14.740" end="20.450" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.740" end="14.890">地</span><span begin="14.990" end="15.360">球</span><span begin="15.360" end="15.680">の</span><span begin="15.680" end="16.130">裏</span><span begin="16.130" end="16.600">側</span><span begin="16.600" end="16.830">ま</span><span begin="16.830" end="17.090">で</span><span begin="17.500" end="17.750">食</span><span begin="17.750" end="17.950">べ</span><span begin="17.950" end="18.200">つ</span><span begin="18.200" end="18.410">く</span><span begin="18.410" end="18.690">さ</span><span begin="18.690" end="18.930">れ</span><span begin="18.930" end="20.450">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">连地球的另一侧都被啃食殆尽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">連地球的另一側都被啃食殆盡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Eaten up all the way to the other side of the earth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지구 반대편까지 다 먹어 치워져서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dévorés jusqu&apos;à l&apos;autre bout de la Terre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Devorados hasta el otro lado de la Tierra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bis zur Rückseite der Erde wurde alles aufgefressen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Devorado até o outro lado da Terra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Divorati fino all&apos;altro lato della Terra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Chikyuu no uragawa made tabetsukusarete</span></p><p begin="21.840" end="27.820" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.840" end="22.130">も</span><span begin="22.130" end="22.300">う</span><span begin="22.300" end="22.360">、</span><span begin="22.360" end="22.680">な</span><span begin="22.680" end="22.740">ん</span><span begin="22.740" end="22.940">だ</span><span begin="22.940" end="23.060">っ</span><span begin="23.060" end="23.320">て</span><span begin="23.320" end="23.530">良</span><span begin="23.530" end="23.750">い</span><span begin="23.750" end="23.980">か</span><span begin="23.980" end="24.180">ら</span><span begin="24.180" end="24.460">生</span><span begin="24.460" end="24.560">の</span><span begin="24.560" end="24.790">実</span><span begin="24.890" end="25.370">感</span><span begin="25.370" end="25.560">が</span><span begin="25.560" end="25.790">欲</span><span begin="25.790" end="26.070">し</span><span begin="26.070" end="27.820">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真是的，怎样都好 给我些活着的实感吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真是的，怎樣都好 給我些活著的實感吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Anything is fine now, I just want the feeling of being alive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이제, 뭐든 좋으니까 살아있다는 실감을 원해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peu importe quoi maintenant, je veux ressentir que je suis en vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ya, no me importa nada así que quiero la sensación de estar vivo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schon, egal was es ist ich will das Gefühl lebendig zu sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Já não importa o que seja, só quero a sensação de estar viva</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ormai, qualsiasi cosa va bene voglio la sensazione di essere viva</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mou, nandatte ii kara sei no jikkan ga hoshii</span></p><p begin="29.740" end="31.860" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.740" end="29.950">ど</span><span begin="29.950" end="30.120">う</span><span begin="30.120" end="30.310">だ</span><span begin="30.310" end="30.440">っ</span><span begin="30.440" end="30.700">て</span><span begin="30.700" end="30.960">い</span><span begin="30.960" end="31.150">い</span><span begin="31.150" end="31.360">の</span><span begin="31.360" end="31.630">か</span><span begin="31.630" end="31.860">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">或许怎样都无所谓吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">或許怎樣都無所謂吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It might not matter anyway</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌 되든 상관없을지도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça n&apos;a peut-être pas d&apos;importance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tal vez no importe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Vielleicht ist es auch egal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Talvez não importe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Forse non importa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dou datte ii no kamo</span></p><p begin="32.060" end="33.910" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.060" end="32.170">他</span><span begin="32.300" end="32.530">人</span><span begin="32.710" end="32.960">の</span><span begin="32.960" end="33.200">こ</span><span begin="33.200" end="33.440">と</span><span begin="33.440" end="33.650">な</span><span begin="33.650" end="33.910">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他人的死活之类</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他人的死活之類</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Things like other people</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다른 사람 일 따위</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les autres et le reste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las cosas de los demás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Angelegenheiten anderer und so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Coisas como as outras pessoas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Delle altre persone</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito no koto nado</span></p><p begin="36.160" end="43.680" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.160" end="36.680">す</span><span begin="36.680" end="37.140">べ</span><span begin="37.140" end="37.730">て</span><span begin="37.870" end="38.320">愛</span><span begin="38.320" end="38.550">だ</span><span begin="38.550" end="38.750">と</span><span begin="38.750" end="38.900">言</span><span begin="38.900" end="39.210">う</span><span begin="39.210" end="39.450">の</span><span begin="39.450" end="39.680">な</span><span begin="39.680" end="40.250">ら</span><span begin="40.250" end="40.280">、</span><span begin="40.610" end="41.090">淀</span><span begin="41.090" end="41.320">み</span><span begin="41.320" end="41.590">な</span><span begin="41.590" end="41.780">い</span><span begin="41.780" end="42.000">も</span><span begin="42.000" end="42.200">の</span><span begin="42.200" end="42.470">で</span><span begin="42.470" end="42.770">あ</span><span begin="42.770" end="42.900">っ</span><span begin="42.900" end="43.150">て</span><span begin="43.150" end="43.380">く</span><span begin="43.380" end="43.680">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若说一切皆是爱，那便请务必纯粹澄澈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若說一切皆是愛，那便請務必純粹澄澈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If you call it all love, please let it be something pure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">모든 것이 사랑이라고 말한다면, 막힘없는 것이어 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si tu dis que tout est amour, fais en sorte que ce soit sans tache</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si dices que todo es amor, por favor que sea algo sin estancamientos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du sagst dass alles Liebe ist, dann lass es etwas Ungetrübtes sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se diz que tudo é amor, que seja algo sem impurezas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se dici che è tutto amore, fa&apos; che sia qualcosa di limpido</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Subete ai da to iu no nara, yodominai mono de atte kure</span></p><p begin="44.050" end="51.780" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.050" end="44.370">ず</span><span begin="44.370" end="44.510">っ</span><span begin="44.510" end="45.220">と</span><span begin="45.220" end="45.680">遠</span><span begin="45.680" end="45.920">く</span><span begin="45.920" end="46.140">の</span><span begin="46.140" end="46.620">方</span><span begin="46.620" end="46.870">に</span><span begin="46.870" end="47.100">あ</span><span begin="47.100" end="47.420">る</span><span begin="47.420" end="47.450">、</span><span begin="47.770" end="48.010">あ</span><span begin="48.010" end="48.170">の</span><span begin="48.170" end="48.670">空</span><span begin="48.670" end="48.940">の</span><span begin="48.940" end="49.350">色</span><span begin="49.350" end="49.570">の</span><span begin="49.570" end="49.700">よ</span><span begin="49.700" end="49.830">う</span><span begin="49.830" end="51.780">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就像那远在天边的，那片天空的颜色一样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就像那遠在天邊的，那片天空的顏色一樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Like the color of that sky, far far away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아득히 먼 곳에 있는, 저 하늘의 색처럼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme la couleur de ce ciel, tout au loin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como el color de ese cielo, que está muy a lo lejos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie die Farbe jenes Himmels, der ganz weit weg ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como a cor daquele céu, que está bem longe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come il colore di quel cielo, che si trova molto lontano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zutto tooku no hou ni aru, ano sora no iro no you ni</span></p><p begin="53.250" end="56.920" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.250" end="53.720">目</span><span begin="53.720" end="54.040">を</span><span begin="54.040" end="54.480">覚</span><span begin="54.480" end="54.880">ま</span><span begin="54.880" end="55.170">せ</span><span begin="55.170" end="55.380">ば</span><span begin="55.380" end="55.930">元</span><span begin="55.930" end="56.320">通</span><span begin="56.320" end="56.920">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">睁开双眼便恢复原状</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">睜開雙眼便恢復原狀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Once I wake up everything is back to normal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">눈을 뜨면 원래대로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si je me réveille tout redeviendra comme avant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si abro los ojos todo volverá a la normalidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich aufwache ist alles beim Alten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eu acordar tudo volta ao normal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se apro gli occhi tutto torna come prima</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Me o samaseba motodoori</span></p><p begin="57.200" end="58.990" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.200" end="57.430">ば</span><span begin="57.430" end="57.780">か</span><span begin="57.780" end="58.030">な</span><span begin="58.130" end="58.600">ま</span><span begin="58.600" end="58.840">ま</span><span begin="58.840" end="58.990">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">依旧是一副愚蠢模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">依舊是一副愚蠢模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Still playing the fool</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바보인 채로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En restant idiote</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sigo siendo idiota</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Immer noch dumm</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Continuando boba</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Restando stupida</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Baka na mama de</span></p><p begin="59.020" end="1:00.470" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.020" end="59.290">く</span><span begin="59.290" end="59.500">ら</span><span begin="59.500" end="59.560">、</span><span begin="59.560" end="59.620">く</span><span begin="59.620" end="59.870">ら</span><span begin="59.870" end="59.900">、</span><span begin="59.900" end="59.990">く</span><span begin="59.990" end="1:00.470">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">晕眩，晕眩，晕眩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">暈眩，暈眩，暈眩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Dizzy, dizzy, dizzy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어질, 어질, 어질</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Étourdie, étourdie, étourdie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mareo, mareo, mareo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schwindlig, schwindlig, schwindlig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tonta, tonta, tonta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Gira, gira, gira</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kura, kura, kura</span></p><p begin="1:00.860" end="1:06.680" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.860" end="1:01.520">言</span><span begin="1:01.520" end="1:01.860">葉</span><span begin="1:01.860" end="1:02.330">よ</span><span begin="1:02.330" end="1:02.570">り</span><span begin="1:02.570" end="1:02.770">も</span><span begin="1:02.770" end="1:02.870">不</span><span begin="1:02.990" end="1:03.590">確</span><span begin="1:03.590" end="1:03.700">か</span><span begin="1:03.700" end="1:03.960">な</span><span begin="1:04.340" end="1:04.820">感</span><span begin="1:04.820" end="1:05.280">情</span><span begin="1:05.280" end="1:05.530">な</span><span begin="1:05.530" end="1:05.740">ら</span><span begin="1:05.980" end="1:06.220">消</span><span begin="1:06.220" end="1:06.460">え</span><span begin="1:06.460" end="1:06.680">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是比言语更不确切的感情 那就消失吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是比言語更不確切的感情 那就消失吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If it&apos;s an emotion more uncertain than words then disappear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말보다도 불확실한 감정이라면 사라져줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si ce sont des sentiments plus incertains que les mots alors disparaissez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si son emociones más inciertas que las palabras desaparezcan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn es ein Gefühl ist das ungewisser als Worte ist dann verschwinde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se for um sentimento mais incerto que as palavras, desapareça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se è un&apos;emozione più incerta delle parole allora scompari</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotoba yori mo futashika na kanjou nara kiete</span></p><p begin="1:06.900" end="1:08.780" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.900" end="1:07.080">も</span><span begin="1:07.080" end="1:07.200">う</span><span begin="1:07.200" end="1:07.230">、</span><span begin="1:07.380" end="1:07.610">い</span><span begin="1:07.610" end="1:07.800">ら</span><span begin="1:08.050" end="1:08.280">な</span><span begin="1:08.280" end="1:08.520">い</span><span begin="1:08.520" end="1:08.780">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我已经不需要了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我已經不需要了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I don&apos;t, need it anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이제, 필요 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n&apos;en veux plus,</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ya, no las necesito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schon, ich brauche es nicht mehr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Já não preciso mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ormai, non ne ho più bisogno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mou, iranai no</span></p><p begin="1:12.000" end="1:15.830" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.000" end="1:12.200">生</span><span begin="1:12.200" end="1:12.580">き</span><span begin="1:12.580" end="1:12.940">て</span><span begin="1:12.940" end="1:13.150">い</span><span begin="1:13.150" end="1:13.420">る</span><span begin="1:13.420" end="1:13.610">よ</span><span begin="1:13.610" end="1:13.830">り</span><span begin="1:13.830" end="1:14.350">楽</span><span begin="1:14.350" end="1:14.690">し</span><span begin="1:14.690" end="1:15.090">そ</span><span begin="1:15.090" end="1:15.800">う</span><span begin="1:15.800" end="1:15.830">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看起来比活着还要快活？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看起來比活著還要快活？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Looks more fun than being alive?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아있는 것보다 즐거워 보여?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça a l&apos;air plus amusant que d&apos;être en vie ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Parece más divertido que estar vivo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieht es spaßiger aus als am Leben zu sein?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parece mais divertido do que estar viva?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra più divertente che essere vivi?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikiteiru yori tanoshisou?</span></p><p begin="1:19.370" end="1:22.900" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.370" end="1:19.590">生</span><span begin="1:19.590" end="1:19.950">き</span><span begin="1:19.950" end="1:20.200">て</span><span begin="1:20.200" end="1:20.510">い</span><span begin="1:20.510" end="1:20.730">る</span><span begin="1:20.730" end="1:20.980">よ</span><span begin="1:20.980" end="1:21.200">り</span><span begin="1:21.200" end="1:21.720">楽</span><span begin="1:21.720" end="1:22.090">し</span><span begin="1:22.090" end="1:22.450">そ</span><span begin="1:22.450" end="1:22.870">う</span><span begin="1:22.870" end="1:22.900">！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看起来比活着还要快活！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看起來比活著還要快活！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Looks more fun than being alive!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아있는 것보다 즐거워 보여!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça a l&apos;air plus amusant que d&apos;être en vie !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Parece más divertido que estar vivo!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieht es spaßiger aus als am Leben zu sein!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parece mais divertido do que estar viva!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra più divertente che essere vivi!</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikiteiru yori tanoshisou!</span></p><p begin="1:26.910" end="1:32.270" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.910" end="1:27.200">雑</span><span begin="1:27.310" end="1:27.720">踏</span><span begin="1:27.720" end="1:27.910">の</span><span begin="1:27.910" end="1:28.360">中</span><span begin="1:28.360" end="1:28.590">で</span><span begin="1:28.590" end="1:28.780">気</span><span begin="1:28.780" end="1:28.970">づ</span><span begin="1:28.970" end="1:29.170">い</span><span begin="1:29.170" end="1:29.450">た</span><span begin="1:29.570" end="1:29.860">レ</span><span begin="1:29.860" end="1:29.990">イ</span><span begin="1:29.990" end="1:30.240">テ</span><span begin="1:30.240" end="1:30.440">ン</span><span begin="1:30.440" end="1:32.270">シ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在熙攘人群中察觉到的延迟</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在熙攘人群中察覺到的延遲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The latency I noticed in the crowd</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">혼잡 속에서 깨달은 레이턴시</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La latence remarquée dans la foule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La latencia que noté en medio de la multitud</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Latenz die ich in der Menschenmenge bemerkte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A latência que percebi no meio da multidão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La latenza notata in mezzo alla folla</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zattou no naka de kizuita reitenshi</span></p><p begin="1:34.340" end="1:36.440" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.340" end="1:34.540">ど</span><span begin="1:34.540" end="1:34.720">う</span><span begin="1:34.720" end="1:34.930">だ</span><span begin="1:34.930" end="1:35.070">っ</span><span begin="1:35.070" end="1:35.340">て</span><span begin="1:35.340" end="1:35.540">い</span><span begin="1:35.540" end="1:35.760">い</span><span begin="1:35.760" end="1:35.990">か</span><span begin="1:35.990" end="1:36.230">も</span><span begin="1:36.230" end="1:36.440">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">或许怎样都无所谓呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">或許怎樣都無所謂呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It might not matter right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌 되든 상관없을지도 몰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça n&apos;a peut-être pas d&apos;importance n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tal vez no importe nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist wohl wirklich egal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Talvez não importe né</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Forse non importa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dou datte ii kamo ne</span></p><p begin="1:36.650" end="1:38.460" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.650" end="1:36.760">他</span><span begin="1:36.880" end="1:37.110">人</span><span begin="1:37.350" end="1:37.570">の</span><span begin="1:37.570" end="1:37.720">こ</span><span begin="1:37.830" end="1:38.070">と</span><span begin="1:38.070" end="1:38.290">な</span><span begin="1:38.290" end="1:38.460">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他人的死活之类</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他人的死活之類</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Things like other people</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다른 사람 일 따위</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les autres et le reste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las cosas de los demás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Angelegenheiten anderer und so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Coisas como as outras pessoas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Delle altre persone</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito no koto nado</span></p><p begin="1:41.230" end="1:43.460" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.230" end="1:41.750">つ</span><span begin="1:41.750" end="1:42.040">ま</span><span begin="1:42.040" end="1:42.130">ん</span><span begin="1:42.130" end="1:42.350">な</span><span begin="1:42.350" end="1:42.450">い</span><span begin="1:42.450" end="1:43.160">話</span><span begin="1:43.160" end="1:43.380">な</span><span begin="1:43.380" end="1:43.460">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是些无聊的话题</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是些無聊的話題</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If it&apos;s a boring story</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">시시한 이야기라면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si c&apos;est une histoire ennuyeuse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si es una historia aburrida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn es eine langweilige Geschichte ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se for uma história chata</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se è una storia noiosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsumannai hanashi nara</span></p><p begin="1:43.500" end="1:47.080" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.500" end="1:43.950">胸</span><span begin="1:43.950" end="1:44.210">に</span><span begin="1:44.210" end="1:44.350">し</span><span begin="1:44.350" end="1:44.620">ま</span><span begin="1:44.620" end="1:44.730">っ</span><span begin="1:44.730" end="1:45.050">と</span><span begin="1:45.050" end="1:45.220">い</span><span begin="1:45.220" end="1:47.080">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就请烂在心里吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就請爛在心裡吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Keep it locked in your chest</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가슴에 담아둬</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Garde-la pour toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Guárdatela en el pecho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Behalte sie für dich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Guarde no seu peito</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tienitela nel cuore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mune ni shimattoite</span></p><p begin="1:49.090" end="1:51.240" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.090" end="1:49.390">ど</span><span begin="1:49.390" end="1:49.500">う</span><span begin="1:49.500" end="1:49.710">だ</span><span begin="1:49.710" end="1:49.840">っ</span><span begin="1:49.840" end="1:50.140">て</span><span begin="1:50.140" end="1:50.340">い</span><span begin="1:50.340" end="1:50.520">い</span><span begin="1:50.520" end="1:50.730">の</span><span begin="1:50.730" end="1:51.020">か</span><span begin="1:51.020" end="1:51.240">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">或许怎样都无所谓吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">或許怎樣都無所謂吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It might not matter anyway</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌 되든 상관없을지도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça n&apos;a peut-être pas d&apos;importance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tal vez no importe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Vielleicht ist es auch egal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Talvez não importe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Forse non importa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dou datte ii no kamo</span></p><p begin="1:51.420" end="1:54.550" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.420" end="1:51.530">他</span><span begin="1:51.690" end="1:51.950">人</span><span begin="1:52.090" end="1:52.370">の</span><span begin="1:52.370" end="1:52.600">こ</span><span begin="1:52.600" end="1:52.830">と</span><span begin="1:52.830" end="1:53.070">な</span><span begin="1:53.070" end="1:54.550">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他人的死活之类</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他人的死活之類</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Things like other people</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다른 사람 일 따위</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les autres et le reste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las cosas de los demás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Angelegenheiten anderer und so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Coisas como as outras pessoas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Delle altre persone</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito no koto nado</span></p><p begin="1:55.550" end="2:03.100" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.550" end="1:56.500">君</span><span begin="1:56.500" end="1:57.010">が</span><span begin="1:57.010" end="1:57.610">答</span><span begin="1:57.610" end="1:57.710">え</span><span begin="1:57.710" end="1:57.930">だ</span><span begin="1:57.930" end="1:58.110">と</span><span begin="1:58.110" end="1:58.250">言</span><span begin="1:58.250" end="1:58.610">う</span><span begin="1:58.610" end="1:58.840">の</span><span begin="1:58.840" end="1:59.050">な</span><span begin="1:59.050" end="1:59.580">ら</span><span begin="1:59.580" end="1:59.610">、</span><span begin="1:59.940" end="2:00.210">つ</span><span begin="2:00.210" end="2:00.470">ま</span><span begin="2:00.470" end="2:00.670">ら</span><span begin="2:00.670" end="2:01.030">な</span><span begin="2:01.030" end="2:01.120">い</span><span begin="2:01.120" end="2:01.560">人</span><span begin="2:01.560" end="2:01.860">で</span><span begin="2:01.860" end="2:02.160">あ</span><span begin="2:02.160" end="2:02.280">っ</span><span begin="2:02.280" end="2:02.510">て</span><span begin="2:02.510" end="2:02.690">欲</span><span begin="2:02.690" end="2:02.910">し</span><span begin="2:02.910" end="2:03.100">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若你说你便是答案，那我希望你是个无趣的人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若你說你便是答案，那我希望你是個無趣的人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If you say you are the answer, I want you to be a boring person</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네가 정답이라고 말한다면, 시시한 사람이길 바라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si tu dis que tu es la réponse, je veux que tu sois quelqu&apos;un d&apos;ennuyeux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si dices que tú eres la respuesta, quiero que seas una persona aburrida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn du sagst dass du die Antwort bist, möchte ich dass du ein langweiliger Mensch bist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se diz que você é a resposta, quero que seja uma pessoa chata</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se dici di essere tu la risposta, vorrei che fossi una persona noiosa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga kotae da to iu no nara, tsumaranai hito de atte hoshii</span></p><p begin="2:03.420" end="2:06.770" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.420" end="2:03.730">き</span><span begin="2:03.730" end="2:03.900">っ</span><span begin="2:03.900" end="2:04.370">と</span><span begin="2:04.370" end="2:04.810">大</span><span begin="2:04.810" end="2:05.070">事</span><span begin="2:05.070" end="2:05.270">に</span><span begin="2:05.270" end="2:05.550">す</span><span begin="2:05.550" end="2:05.990">る</span><span begin="2:05.990" end="2:06.240">か</span><span begin="2:06.240" end="2:06.510">ら</span><span begin="2:06.510" end="2:06.740">ね</span><span begin="2:06.740" end="2:06.770">！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我一定会好好珍视的！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我一定會好好珍視的！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I will surely cherish you!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">분명 소중히 할 테니까!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;en prendrai sûrement soin tu sais !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Seguro que lo atesoraré!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde dich sicher gut behandeln!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com certeza vou cuidar bem!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché ne avrò sicuramente cura!</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kitto daiji ni suru kara ne!</span></p><p begin="2:07.120" end="2:11.330" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.120" end="2:07.600">悪</span><span begin="2:07.600" end="2:07.830">い</span><span begin="2:07.830" end="2:08.310">夢</span><span begin="2:08.310" end="2:08.500">の</span><span begin="2:08.500" end="2:08.980">続</span><span begin="2:08.980" end="2:09.210">き</span><span begin="2:09.210" end="2:11.330">も…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就连那噩梦的后续也…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就連那噩夢的後續也…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even the continuation of a bad dream...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나쁜 꿈의 다음도…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même de la suite de ce mauvais rêve...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso la continuación de la pesadilla...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch die Fortsetzung des bösen Traums...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Até a continuação do pesadelo...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche del seguito del brutto sogno…</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Warui yume no tsuzuki mo...</span></p><p begin="2:12.630" end="2:17.820" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.630" end="2:13.140">枯</span><span begin="2:13.140" end="2:13.490">れ</span><span begin="2:13.490" end="2:13.840">た</span><span begin="2:13.840" end="2:14.320">声</span><span begin="2:14.320" end="2:14.540">で</span><span begin="2:14.540" end="2:14.710">も</span><span begin="2:14.710" end="2:15.300">叫</span><span begin="2:15.300" end="2:15.530">ば</span><span begin="2:15.530" end="2:15.680">せ</span><span begin="2:15.680" end="2:17.790">て</span><span begin="2:17.790" end="2:17.820">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕声嘶力竭也让我呐喊吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕聲嘶力竭也讓我吶喊吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let me scream even with a withered voice?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">쉬어버린 목소리라도 외치게 해줄래?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisse-moi crier même avec une voix brisée ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Me dejas gritar incluso con una voz marchita?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich schreien auch mit heiserer Stimme?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me deixa gritar mesmo com a voz rouca?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fammi urlare anche con la voce rauca?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kareta koe demo sakebasete?</span></p><p begin="2:16.290" end="2:21.310" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:16.290" end="2:17.090">腐</span><span begin="2:17.090" end="2:17.280">っ</span><span begin="2:17.280" end="2:17.550">て</span><span begin="2:17.550" end="2:17.830">な</span><span begin="2:17.830" end="2:17.970">い</span><span begin="2:17.970" end="2:18.200">で</span><span begin="2:18.450" end="2:18.730">こ</span><span begin="2:18.730" end="2:18.840">っ</span><span begin="2:18.840" end="2:19.130">ち</span><span begin="2:19.130" end="2:19.380">を</span><span begin="2:19.380" end="2:19.590">見</span><span begin="2:19.590" end="2:21.310">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别在那腐烂了看着我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別在那腐爛了看著我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t rot away and look at me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">썩어있지 말고 이쪽을 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne pourris pas et regarde par ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No te pudras y mírame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verrotte nicht und sieh mich an</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não fique apodrecendo e olhe para cá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non marcire guarda da questa parte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kusattenaide kocchi o mite</span></p><p begin="2:21.850" end="2:25.790" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.850" end="2:22.180">き</span><span begin="2:22.180" end="2:22.380">み</span><span begin="2:22.380" end="2:22.800">が</span><span begin="2:22.800" end="2:23.060">す</span><span begin="2:23.060" end="2:23.720">き</span><span begin="2:23.720" end="2:24.000">だ</span><span begin="2:24.000" end="2:25.790">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我喜欢你啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我喜歡你啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I love you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너를 좋아해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je t&apos;aime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te quiero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich liebe dich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu gosto de você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ti amo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga suki da yo</span></p><p begin="2:41.690" end="2:45.720" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.690" end="2:42.220">ど</span><span begin="2:42.220" end="2:42.680">ん</span><span begin="2:42.680" end="2:43.090">な</span><span begin="2:43.370" end="2:44.090">光</span><span begin="2:44.090" end="2:44.280">を</span><span begin="2:44.280" end="2:44.760">食</span><span begin="2:44.760" end="2:44.980">べ</span><span begin="2:44.980" end="2:45.230">て</span><span begin="2:45.230" end="2:45.720">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论吞噬怎样的光芒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論吞噬怎樣的光芒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No matter what kind of light I eat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어떤 빛을 먹어도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peu importe la lumière que tu dévores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sin importar qué luz coma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Egal welches Licht du isst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não importa quanta luz você coma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualsiasi luce tu mangi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Donna hikari o tabetemo</span></p><p begin="2:46.140" end="2:49.280" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:46.140" end="2:46.620">眠</span><span begin="2:46.620" end="2:46.850">れ</span><span begin="2:46.850" end="2:47.150">な</span><span begin="2:47.150" end="2:47.330">い</span><span begin="2:47.330" end="2:47.770">夜</span><span begin="2:47.770" end="2:47.990">が</span><span begin="2:47.990" end="2:48.330">あ</span><span begin="2:48.330" end="2:48.440">っ</span><span begin="2:48.440" end="2:48.670">た</span><span begin="2:48.670" e