"2:51.720">か</span><span begin="2:51.720" end="2:52.130">な</span><span begin="2:52.130" end="2:52.380">し</span><span begin="2:52.380" end="2:52.650">み</span><span begin="2:52.650" end="2:52.870">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论怎样的悲伤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論怎樣的悲傷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No matter what kind of sadness</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어떤 슬픔도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Peu importe la tristesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cualquier tristeza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jegliche Traurigkeit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Qualquer tristeza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Qualsiasi tristezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Donna kanashimi mo</span></p><p begin="2:53.250" end="2:57.310" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.250" end="2:53.720">ほ</span><span begin="2:53.720" end="2:54.030">そ</span><span begin="2:54.030" end="2:54.260">い</span><span begin="2:54.260" end="2:54.480">う</span><span begin="2:54.480" end="2:54.690">で</span><span begin="2:54.690" end="2:54.890">の</span><span begin="2:54.890" end="2:55.120">な</span><span begin="2:55.120" end="2:55.500">か</span><span begin="2:55.500" end="2:57.310">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">都拥入这纤细的双臂中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">都擁入這纖細的雙臂中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In those thin arms</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가녀린 팔 안에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans ces bras fins</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dentro de estos brazos delgados</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In diesen schmalen Armen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dentro destes braços finos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tra queste braccia sottili</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hosoi ude no naka ni</span></p><p begin="2:58.800" end="3:02.440" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.800" end="2:59.270">目</span><span begin="2:59.270" end="2:59.570">を</span><span begin="2:59.570" end="2:59.970">覚</span><span begin="2:59.970" end="3:00.310">ま</span><span begin="3:00.310" end="3:00.450">し</span><span begin="3:00.450" end="3:00.710">て</span><span begin="3:00.710" end="3:00.860">も</span><span begin="3:00.860" end="3:01.470">程</span><span begin="3:01.470" end="3:01.880">遠</span><span begin="3:01.880" end="3:02.440">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">纵使醒来也依旧遥不可及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">縱使醒來也依舊遙不可及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I wake up it&apos;s so far away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">눈을 떠도 아득히 멀어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je me réveille on est bien loin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si despierto estoy muy lejos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn ich aufwache ist es noch weit entfernt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo acordando estou longe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se apro gli occhi è molto lontano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Me o samashitemo hodotooi</span></p><p begin="3:02.720" end="3:04.520" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:02.720" end="3:03.230">白</span><span begin="3:03.230" end="3:03.340">痴</span><span begin="3:03.340" end="3:03.690">の</span><span begin="3:03.690" end="3:04.040">ま</span><span begin="3:04.150" end="3:04.380">ま</span><span begin="3:04.380" end="3:04.520">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">依旧是一副痴傻模样</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">依舊是一副痴傻模樣</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Still remaining an idiot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">백치인 채로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En restant idiote</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sigo en la idiotez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Immer noch idiotisch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Continuando idiota</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Restando idiota</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hakuchi no mama de</span></p><p begin="3:04.580" end="3:06.040" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:04.580" end="3:04.840">く</span><span begin="3:04.840" end="3:05.040">ら</span><span begin="3:05.040" end="3:05.150">、</span><span begin="3:05.150" end="3:05.210">く</span><span begin="3:05.210" end="3:05.390">ら</span><span begin="3:05.390" end="3:05.440">、</span><span begin="3:05.440" end="3:05.530">く</span><span begin="3:05.530" end="3:06.040">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">晕眩，晕眩，晕眩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">暈眩，暈眩，暈眩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Dizzy, dizzy, dizzy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어질, 어질, 어질</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Étourdie, étourdie, étourdie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mareo, mareo, mareo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schwindlig, schwindlig, schwindlig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tonta, tonta, tonta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Gira, gira, gira</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kura, kura, kura</span></p><p begin="3:06.430" end="3:14.310" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:06.430" end="3:07.410">身体</span><span begin="3:07.410" end="3:07.850">よ</span><span begin="3:07.850" end="3:08.080">り</span><span begin="3:08.080" end="3:08.260">も</span><span begin="3:08.260" end="3:08.420">不</span><span begin="3:08.530" end="3:09.110">確</span><span begin="3:09.110" end="3:09.230">か</span><span begin="3:09.230" end="3:09.590">な</span><span begin="3:09.890" end="3:10.380">も</span><span begin="3:10.380" end="3:10.790">の</span><span begin="3:10.790" end="3:11.050">以</span><span begin="3:11.050" end="3:11.550">外</span><span begin="3:11.550" end="3:11.790">な</span><span begin="3:11.790" end="3:12.000">ら</span><span begin="3:12.000" end="3:12.130">も</span><span begin="3:12.130" end="3:12.230">う</span><span begin="3:12.230" end="3:12.260">、</span><span begin="3:12.460" end="3:12.600">も</span><span begin="3:12.600" end="3:12.700">う</span><span begin="3:12.930" end="3:13.150">い</span><span begin="3:13.150" end="3:13.390">ら</span><span begin="3:13.600" end="3:13.820">な</span><span begin="3:13.820" end="3:14.060">い</span><span begin="3:14.060" end="3:14.310">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若非比躯体更为暧昧之物 我便已不再需要</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若非比軀體更為曖昧之物 我便已不再需要</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Anything other than things more uncertain than the body, I don&apos;t, I don&apos;t need anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">신체보다도 불확실한 것 이외라면 이제, 이제 필요 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À part ce qui est plus incertain que le corps, je n&apos;en veux plus, plus du tout</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aparte de las cosas más inciertas que el cuerpo ya, ya no necesito nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Alles außer Dingen die ungewisser sind als der Körper brauche ich schon, schon nicht mehr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se não for algo mais incerto que o corpo, eu já, já não preciso mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tranne ciò che è più incerto del corpo ormai, ormai non ne ho più bisogno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Karada yori mo futashika na mono igai nara mou, mou iranai no</span></p><p begin="3:17.530" end="3:21.800" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:17.530" end="3:17.750">生</span><span begin="3:17.750" end="3:18.130">き</span><span begin="3:18.130" end="3:18.480">て</span><span begin="3:18.480" end="3:18.720">い</span><span begin="3:18.720" end="3:18.970">る</span><span begin="3:18.970" end="3:19.170">よ</span><span begin="3:19.170" end="3:19.360">り</span><span begin="3:19.360" end="3:19.900">楽</span><span begin="3:19.900" end="3:20.250">し</span><span begin="3:20.250" end="3:20.570">そ</span><span begin="3:20.570" end="3:21.770">う</span><span begin="3:21.770" end="3:21.800">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看起来比活着还要快活？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看起來比活著還要快活？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Looks more fun than being alive?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아있는 것보다 즐거워 보여?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça a l&apos;air plus amusant que d&apos;être en vie ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Parece más divertido que estar vivo?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieht es spaßiger aus als am Leben zu sein?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parece mais divertido do que estar viva?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra più divertente che essere vivi?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikiteiru yori tanoshisou?</span></p><p begin="3:24.910" end="3:30.720" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:24.910" end="3:25.130">言</span><span begin="3:25.130" end="3:25.460">わ</span><span begin="3:25.460" end="3:25.830">せ</span><span begin="3:25.830" end="3:26.150">な</span><span begin="3:26.150" end="3:26.270">い</span><span begin="3:26.270" end="3:26.500">で</span><span begin="3:26.500" end="3:26.690">よ</span><span begin="3:26.690" end="3:26.720">、</span><span begin="3:26.720" end="3:26.980">恥</span><span begin="3:26.980" end="3:27.460">ず</span><span begin="3:27.460" end="3:27.880">か</span><span begin="3:27.880" end="3:30.720">しい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别逼我说出来啊，怪难为情的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別逼我說出來啊，怪難為情的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t make me say it, it&apos;s embarrassing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말하게 하지 마, 부끄러워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne me le fais pas dire, c&apos;est embarrassant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No me hagas decirlo, me da vergüenza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich das nicht sagen, es ist peinlich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não me faça dizer, é vergonhoso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non farmelo dire, è imbarazzante</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Iwasenaide yo, hazukashii</span></p><p begin="3:32.300" end="3:38.400" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:32.300" end="3:32.500">生</span><span begin="3:32.500" end="3:32.880">き</span><span begin="3:32.880" end="3:33.150">て</span><span begin="3:33.150" end="3:33.420">い</span><span begin="3:33.420" end="3:33.690">る</span><span begin="3:33.690" end="3:33.880">よ</span><span begin="3:33.880" end="3:34.120">り</span><span begin="3:34.120" end="3:34.780">楽</span><span begin="3:34.780" end="3:35.260">し</span><span begin="3:35.260" end="3:36.250">そ</span><span begin="3:36.250" end="3:38.370">う</span><span begin="3:38.370" end="3:38.400">！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看起来比活着还要快活！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看起來比活著還要快活！</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Looks more fun than being alive!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아있는 것보다 즐거워 보여!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ça a l&apos;air plus amusant que d&apos;être en vie !</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¡Parece más divertido que estar vivo!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieht es spaßiger aus als am Leben zu sein!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parece mais divertido do que estar viva!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra più divertente che essere vivi!</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikiteiru yori tanoshisou!</span></p><p begin="3:39.700" end="3:43.480" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:39.700" end="3:39.910">言</span><span begin="3:39.910" end="3:40.270">わ</span><span begin="3:40.270" end="3:40.630">せ</span><span begin="3:40.630" end="3:40.960">な</span><span begin="3:40.960" end="3:41.090">い</span><span begin="3:41.090" end="3:41.330">で</span><span begin="3:41.330" end="3:41.520">よ</span><span begin="3:41.520" end="3:41.550">、</span><span begin="3:41.550" end="3:41.720">言</span><span begin="3:41.720" end="3:42.100">わ</span><span begin="3:42.100" end="3:42.450">せ</span><span begin="3:42.450" end="3:42.630">な</span><span begin="3:42.630" end="3:42.890">い</span><span begin="3:42.890" end="3:43.140">で</span><span begin="3:43.140" end="3:43.480">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别逼我说出来啊，别逼我说出来啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別逼我說出來啊，別逼我說出來啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t make me say it, don&apos;t make me say it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말하게 하지 마, 말하게 하지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne me le fais pas dire, ne me le fais pas dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No me hagas decirlo, no me hagas decirlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich das nicht sagen, lass mich das nicht sagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não me faça dizer, não me faça dizer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non farmelo dire, non farmelo dire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Iwasenaide yo, iwasenaide yo</span></p></div></body></tt>